msgctxt "2756"
msgid ""
"斎藤さん。\n"
"先日、豊臣家残党の集落で相対した曽田地より\n"
"再戦を願う果たし状が来ています。"
msgstr ""
"Mr. Saito. The other day, a letter of fulfillment\n"
"praying for a rematch has arrived\n"
"from Sodaji, who faced the village\n"
"of the Toyotomi clan remnants."

msgctxt "2845"
msgid "再戦？"
msgstr "rematch?"

msgctxt "2852"
msgid ""
"三番隊に敗れてからというもの\n"
"子分たちとともに厳しい修行に明け暮れ\n"
"剣の新たな境地へ達したようです。"
msgstr ""
"After being defeated by the 3rd corps, it\n"
"seems that he and his minions have gone\n"
"through rigorous training and reached\n"
"a new level of sword."

msgctxt "2953"
msgid ""
"真の武の心にも目覚め\n"
"恥を忍んで、一人の侍として\n"
"斎藤さん、そして三番隊に手合せ願いたい、と。"
msgstr ""
"Awakening to the true spirit of Takeshi,\n"
"I would like to ask Mr. Saito and the\n"
"third corps to work as a samurai."

msgctxt "3048"
msgid ""
"……そうか。\n"
"あれだけの実力を持つ男だ。\n"
"つまらん罠ではなく、本当に力を試したいんだろう。"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3139"
msgid ""
"斎藤さんの都合のつく時でいいとのことです。\n"
"もし、時間ができましたら\n"
"ご案内しますので、私にご用命ください。"
msgstr ""
"It's okay when Mr. Saito's convenience comes.\n"
"If you have time, I'll let you know,\n"
"so please ask me."

msgctxt "3248"
msgid ""
"出兵の際は、先方に連絡を入れます。\n"
"私の気づかないところで出兵されても、向こうの\n"
"準備ができてないかもしれないのでご注意を。"
msgstr ""
"When sending troops, we will contact the\n"
"other party. Please note that you may\n"
"not be ready for the other side even if\n"
"you are dispatched without my knowledge."

msgctxt "3373"
msgid ""
"「出兵」より「豊臣秀武を倒せ」を選択することで\n"
"曽田地の再挑戦を受けることができます。\n"
"\n"
"特殊任務ですので十分に準備して挑みましょう。"
msgstr ""
"You can take the re-challenge of Sodachi\n"
"by selecting \"Defeat Toyotomi Hidetake\"\n"
"from \"Send troops\". This is a special\n"
"mission, so be prepared and challenge yourself."

msgctxt "3508"
msgid ""
"<Color:7>【注意】<Color:Default>\n"
"PS Vitaでは特殊任務を受けることはできません。\n"
"\n"
"「豊臣秀武を倒せ」を選択しても\n"
"前回までと同じ任務に挑むことになります。"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3664"
msgid ""
"ああ、わかった。\n"
"準備ができたら、声をかける。"
msgstr "Oh, I understand. Call out when you're ready."

msgctxt "3711"
msgid ""
"斎藤さん！\n"
"亜門玄丈斎と名乗る者から果たし状が！"
msgstr ""
"Saito-san! A letter of fulfillment from\n"
"a person who calls himself Amon Genjosai!"

msgctxt "3760"
msgid ""
"亜門……\n"
"やはり、来たか。"
msgstr "Amon …… Did you come after all?"

msgctxt "3787"
msgid ""
"確か、かの豪傑、曽田地を無力化したという\n"
"腕利きの暗殺者ですよね？\n"
"三番隊を招集しましょうか？"
msgstr ""
"Certainly, he is a skillful assassin who\n"
"has incapacitated Sodaji, the great master,\n"
"isn't he? Shall we convene the third\n"
"party?"

msgctxt "3882"
msgid ""
"いや……\n"
"亜門との決闘には、俺一人で行く。"
msgstr "No ... I go alone to the duel with Amon."

msgctxt "3925"
msgid ""
"ええ!?\n"
"斎藤さんの腕を疑うわけじゃないですが\n"
"わざわざ一人で行かなくても……"
msgstr ""
"Yeah !? I don't doubt Mr. Saito's arm, but\n"
"even if I don't bother to go alone ..."

msgctxt "4002"
msgid ""
"危険は承知の上だ。\n"
"それでも俺は、あいつと１対１で決着を\n"
"つけなくちゃならない。"
msgstr ""
"I know the danger. Still, I have to settle\n"
"one-on-one with him."

msgctxt "4083"
msgid ""
"曽田地の雪辱を果たすためもあるが……\n"
"何より、あの亜門という男には\n"
"不思議な因果のようなものを感じる。"
msgstr ""
"There is also a way to fulfill the snow\n"
"humiliation of Sodaji, but above all, that\n"
"man named Amon feels something like\n"
"a mysterious cause and effect."

msgctxt "4186"
msgid "それを１対１で剣を交えて確かめたい。"
msgstr "I want to confirm it one-on-one with a sword."

msgctxt "4223"
msgid ""
"……そうですか。\n"
"そこまで強い信念をお持ちなら止めはしません。"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4286"
msgid ""
"亜門は\n"
"「夜の更けた頃合い、清水の舞台にて待つ」\n"
"と果たし状に書いています。"
msgstr ""
"Amon wrote in a letter saying, \"Wait at\n"
"the stage of Kiyomizu at the end of the\n"
"night.\""

msgctxt "4363"
msgid ""
"夜に清水寺だな。\n"
"わかった。"
msgstr "It's Kiyomizu-dera at night. all right."

